{"hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"These "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":" are defined for components and refer to semantic tokens or raw tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"They can be seen as a kind of bridge between components and in the end primitive values of the design kit."}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"code":["🧬 Core version: 1.9.0"],"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Thus if a component need to change for example its "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"background color"}]},{"type":"text","text":", and if a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component token"}]},{"type":"text","text":" is used for it, then only the value of this "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"token"}]},{"type":"text","text":" should be changed without any modification on the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component"}]},{"type":"text","text":" definition."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components"}]},{"type":"text","text":" use "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":" exposed through the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"theme"}]},{"type":"text","text":" thanks to token providers to get their style values."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components tokens are defined and gathered inside "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift protocol"}]},{"type":"text","text":" so as to be exposed then through implementation of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" thanks to dedicated tokens providers."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because we choose to split responsabilities and objects into their own modules, we faced troubles to make possible for children themes or providers to override properties declared in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"protocols"}]},{"type":"text","text":" and defined in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"extensions"}]},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"That is the reason why tokens are exposed as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@objc open"},{"type":"text","text":" to be available and overridable anywhere."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Example with "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSTokensComponent\/documentation\/OUDSTokensComponent\/ButtonComponentTokens","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":":"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Declare some component tokens for buttons with properties they must apply","public protocol ButtonComponentTokens {","    var sizeMaxHeightIconOnly: SizeSemanticToken { get }","    var buttonBorderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { get }","    var buttonBorderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { get }","    var colorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { get }","    var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { get }","}","","\/\/ There is an existing provider for such tokens","open class OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider { }","","\/\/ Define the components tokens exposed through the theme thanks to provider","extension OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider: ButtonComponentTokens {","","    \/\/ Raw tokens can be used","","    @objc open var sizeMaxHeightIconOnly: SizeSemanticToken { DimensionRawTokens._600 }","    ","    \/\/ And also semantic tokens","","    @objc open var buttonBorderWidthDefault: BorderWidthSemanticToken { borders.widthThicker }","    @objc open var buttonBorderRadius: BorderRadiusSemanticToken { borders.radiusMedium }","    @objc open var colorBgDefaultPressedMono: MultipleColorSemanticTokens { colors.repositoryOpacityBlackHigher }","    @objc open var spacePaddingBlock: SpaceSemanticToken { spaces.paddingInlineSpacious }","}","","\/\/ This provider is then exposed through OUDSTheme as an AllButtonComponentTokensProvider"]},{"level":2,"anchor":"How-to-use-component-tokens","text":"How to use component tokens","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In fact, the component tokens are declared and gathered in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Swift protocol"}]},{"type":"text","text":" so as to force any theme to implement them, and also to allow any theme to expose such properties whathever the implementation of the theme is, across providers."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Because "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":" have for values "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"raw tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"semantic tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":", and in the end for values primitive types, and all these tokens are declared with "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"type aliases"}]},{"type":"text","text":" refering all together, you can handle a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component token"}]},{"type":"text","text":" directly in your view because the final value will be used."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Thus, get the theme and call the needed property with some helpers."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct SomeView: View {","","    @Environment(\\.theme) private var theme \/\/ Supposed you used in your root view the `OUDSThemeableView` to register the theme","    @Environment(\\.colorScheme) private var colorScheme","","    var body: some View {","        Button {","            \/\/ Some action","        } label: {","            Text(\"Some label\")","                .cornerRadius(theme.button.buttonBorderRadius)","        }","        .padding(.leading, theme.button.spacePaddingInlineChevronStart)","        .padding(.trailing, theme.button.spacePaddingInlineChevronEnd)","        .background(theme.button.colorBgStrongEnabledMono)","        .overlay(","            RoundedRectangle(cornerRadius: theme.button.buttonBorderRadius)","                .stroke(Color.blue, lineWidth: theme.button.buttonBorderWidthDefault)","        )","    }","\/*","    - The theme provides border semantic tokens \"buttonBorderRadius\" and \"buttonBorderWidthDefault\"","    - The theme provides a color semantic token \"colorBgStrongEnabledMono\"","    - The theme provides spaces semantic token \"spacePaddingInlineChevronStart\" and \"spacePaddingInlineChevronEnd\"","*\/","}","","\/\/ Do not forget in your app to use the `OUDSThemeableView` for your theme, e.g. `OrangeTheme`","@main","struct DesignToolbox: App {","","    var body: some Scene {","        WindowGroup {","            OUDSThemeableView(theme: OrangeTheme()) {","                \/\/ Your root view","                ...","            }","        }","    }","}"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The components tokens are wrapped in tokens provider acessible through the themes:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"rows":[[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Components tokens provider"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Target component"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bar"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For bars components like bottom and navigation bars"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"badge"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For badges like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSBadge"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"button"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For buttons like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSButton"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"bulletList"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For list of elements with bullets"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"checkbox"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For checkboxes like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckbox"},{"type":"text","text":", "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSCheckboxItem"},{"type":"text","text":" and their indeterminate variants"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"chip"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For chips like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSuggestionChip"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSFilterChip"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"controlItem"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Shared and used for switch, checkbox and radio items layouts"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"divider"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For dividers like "},{"code":"OUDSHorizontalDivider","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"OUDSVerticalDivider","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"icon"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For components containing icons like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTag"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"link","type":"text"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For links like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSLink","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"pinCodeInput"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"quantityInput"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"radioButton"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For radio components like "},{"code":"OUDSRadio","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"OUDSRadioItem","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"selectInput"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"skeleton"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"switch"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For switch components like "},{"code":"OUDSSwitch","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSSwitchItem"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"tag"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For tag components like "},{"code":"OUDSTag","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"inputTag"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For input tag components like "},{"code":"OUDSInputTag","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"textArea"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For text area components like "},{"code":"OUDSTextArea","type":"codeVoice"}]}]],[[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"textInput"}]}],[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"For text field input components like "},{"code":"OUDSTextInput","type":"codeVoice"}]}]]],"type":"table","header":"row"}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbo